Translation and modification policy
-----------------------------------

MoonBit files or blocks translated line-by-line or structurally from Why3,
and test-only OCaml reference adapters derived from its internals, must retain
the corresponding Why3 copyright notice, identify their pinned upstream
source paths, and record the translation or last semantic modification date.
The checked-in translated-file manifest is the machine-readable source of
truth for this attribution and is validated by CI. New translated files or
adapters must be added to that manifest in the same change.

